  "prompt": "How much salary can expect as a test engineer in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "The salary for a **Test Engineer** in **Hyderabad** can vary based on factors such as experience level, skills, company size, and industry sector. Here\u2019s an approximate range as of **2023**:\n\n- **Fresher (0-2 years of experience)**: \u20b92.5 LPA to \u20b95 LPA  \n- **Mid-Level (2-5 years of experience)**: \u20b95 LPA to \u20b910 LPA  \n- **Senior-Level (5+ years of experience)**: \u20b910 LPA to \u20b918 LPA or more  \n\n**Factors Influencing Salary**:  \n1. **Technical Skills**: Proficiency in tools like Selenium, JMeter, automation testing, performance testing, etc., can increase salary.  \n2. **Certifications**: Certifications like ISTQB, CSTE, or others can add value.  \n3. **Domain Expertise**: Experience in specific domains like healthcare, finance, or e-commerce can command higher pay.  \n4. **Company Type**: MNCs or large IT firms like TCS, Infosys, or Accenture typically pay higher than startups or mid-sized companies.  \n\n**Note**: These figures are approximate and can vary based on market conditions and individual negotiations.  \n\nLet me know if you'd like more details!",
